#include<bits/stdc++.h>
#include<ctype.h>
using namespace std;
int main () {
	string s1,s2;
	int t;
	cin >> t;
	while ( t-- ) {
		cin>>s1>>s2;
		int i;
		for ( i=0 ; s1[i] != '\0' ; i++ ) {
            if ( s1[i] >='a' && s1[i] <='z' ) {
                s1[i] = s1[i] - 32;
            }
		}
		for ( i=0 ; s2[i]!='\0' ; i++ ) {
            if ( s2[i] >='a' && s2[i] <='z' ) {
                s2[i] = s2[i] - 32;
            }
		}
		if ( s1 < s2 )
			printf("first\n");
		else if ( s1 > s2 )
			printf ("second\n");
		else
			printf ( "equal\n");
	}
	return 0;
}
